                    <div class="tab">
                        <div class="tab-wrap">
                            <label for="tab-0">8 Delivery and Storage</label>
                            <div class="tab-content">
                                <p>8.1 We will aim to ensure that all Goods which we receive at your GlobalParcelForward Address are forwarded to your Delivery Address (by way of the Forwarding Service) as soon as possible after receiving your instructions and payment to do so. Goods will normally be forwarded within 48 hours of payment, although it may take longer where we, acting reasonably, suspect that Restricted Goods or Prohibited Goods have been sent to us, or that the Goods may be fraudulent or otherwise unsuitable for export. Delivery times for the Forwarding Service vary according to your DeliveryAddress and the Courier you select, but should take no longer than 10 business days (excluding time spent in customs which is beyond our control) from the date on which we dispatch the Goods to you. Deliveries may require your signature to confirm receipt.</p>
                                <p>8.2 We may, prior to dispatching the Goods to your Delivery Address (by way of the Forwarding Service) and in our discretion, contact you to offer you the option of receiving the Forwarding Service by way of a low cost or pallet based service as opposed to a normal Courier. Where you agree to receiving the Forwarding Service in this way, we will agree with you an alternative Forwarding Fee before we dispatch the Goods to your Delivery Address. When using this low cost or pallet based service, your delivery time should not exceed 30 business days. We will not accept any liability for the loss, damage or destruction of Goods after they have been delivered to you.</p>
                                <p>8.3 We will store Goods which we receive at your GlobalParcelForward Address for up to 30 days without charge whilst we await your instructions to ship and your payment for the Forwarding Service. After this time we will charge a daily storage fee for each package we have stored beyond 30 days. The fee for each package will accrue daily until the package is shipped or disposed of. The fee we charge for storage is set out on the Site or in an email we send you before the charge is incurred.</p>
                                <P>8.4 You agree that the following can be treated by us as Abandoned Goods:</P>
                                <P>8.4.1 Goods that have been stored for more than 12 months;</P>
                                <P>8.4.2 Goods that have been stored for more than 6 months since the last full settlement of storage fees by you;</P>
                                <P>8.4.3 Goods that have been stored for more than 6 months after which we have contacted you by email regarding those Goods but had no reply from you within 3 weeks;</P>
                                <P>8.4.4 Goods who's owner cannot be identified within 4 weeks of receipt despite commercially reasonable efforts by us to identify the owner; and</P>
                                <P>8.4.5 Any and all Goods we hold for you if you fail to settle undisputed invoices within 60 days for any services we have provided or if you have committed or attempted to commit fraud in connection with the Goods or our services.</P>
                                <P>8.5 You authorise us to dispose of Abandoned Goods in any manner we choose.</P>
