                            <div class="tab-content">
                                <p>10.1 Subject to the remaining provisions of this condition 10, in relation to each consignment of
                                  Goods we receive from a Supplier or order on your behalf by way of the Personal Shopper or
                                  Distribution Service, our liability to you in contract, tort (including negligence), breach of statutory
                                  duty or otherwise shall not exceed the lesser of the:</p>
                                <p>10.1.1 repair or replacement cost of the Goods contained in that consignment;</p>
