                                <P>10.1.3 £500 (five hundred pounds sterling).</P>
                                <P>10.2 Where you have indicated on the Site that you would like a consignment of Goods to be insured
                                  whilst it is in the care of the Courier, we will arrange for our insurance policy to cover those Goods.
                                  The insurance will be provided to us by a third party insurer.</P>
                                <P>10.3 Where you place an order with a Supplier for delivery to your GlobalParcelForward Address, it is
                                  your responsibility to ensure that the Supplier is given the correct GlobalParcelForward Address. We
                                  shall not be responsible for any incorrectly labelled deliveries of Goods. We shall only arrange for
                                  our insurance policy to cover Goods where you have indicated in the format of your
