                                  held liable for any mistakes in labelling made by the Supplier.</P>
                                <P>10.4 The cost of taking out any such insurance will include our administration fee for arranging that
                                  insurance. That administration fee, and the overall cost of taking out such insurance is set out on the
                                  Site. If you indicate on the Site that you have read and agree these Terms of Trade, you will also
                                  indicate that you have read and agree the insurance policy's Policy Summary , Insurance Schedule
                                  and Insurance Conditions, each of which may be amended from time to time. It is your responsibility
                                  to check the terms of the insurance set out in those documents (including the specific exclusions)
