                                  material facts and circumstances relevant to the insurance cover, you should notify us of them
                                  immediately after placing your order with the Supplier. You may request that we cancel the
                                  insurance at any time before the collection of your Goods from us by the Courier.</P>
                                <P>10.5 If you would like us to make a claim on the insurance policy on our behalf, you should notify us
                                  within 14 days of actual or scheduled delivery of the Goods (whichever is earlier). We will then make
                                  a claim on our policy on your behalf within the 30 day period under the policy. You will be required
                                  to cooperate fully with us, and any person appointed by the insurer or Courier, in respect of the
                                  claim.</P>
                                <p>10.6 If the claim is rejected by the insurer, you agree that we shall have no liability to you in respect
                                  of that claim.</p>
                                <p>10.7 The option to repair, replace or compensate you for lost or damaged Goods is at our discretion.</p>
                                <p>10.8 Nothing in this Agreement will limit or exclude our liability to you for death or personal injury
                                  resulting from our negligence, fraud or fraudulent misrepresentation.</p>
